{
  "description": "Headless XP/progression mechanic: grants xp when the enemy survivor count drops (UNITS_CHANGED), and on reaching xpToNext levels up — raising the threshold and emitting a HEAL reward the grid-tactics authority applies. Owns only xp/xpToNext/level (+ kill baseline); never writes units.",
